From 089520fee8bdbeccc9b7191e79d4014469845ab5 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Vasu Bhatia <git@vbh.ai>
Date: Mon, 27 Apr 2026 13:32:09 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] eink: add EinkCenterController overlay and EinkPresetManager

EinkCenterController is a CoreStartable that owns the E-Ink Center
overlay window. It listens for ACTION_EINK_GESTURE broadcasts from
PhoneWindowManager and toggles a bottom-sheet panel with step controls
for cold/warm frontlight, a 2x2 refresh-mode selector, and up to six
preset buttons. EinkPresetManager persists named presets to
Settings.System. EinkModule wires both into Dagger.

Change-Id: I110ff6c07630ec05b9cb2ff38db70f702c1c0eb1
---
